node.text:
GIVEAWAY!! We teamed up with @yeti, @flyingembersbrew & @fableticsmen to bring you the ultimate summer pool party giveaway. Enter to win:
•   FUNBOY Giant Cabana Dayclub 
•   YETI Hopper Flip 18 soft cooler + YETI Rambler 36oz. bottle,
•   $200 Flying Embers hard kombucha gift card
•   Two pairs of the all-new #GymToSwim One Short. 
 
How to enter: 
1. Follow @Funboy, @Yeti, @Fableticsmen, and @FlyingEmbersBrew
2. Like this post
3. Tag 3 friends below with #Sweepstakes We’ll announce the winner via DM on 8/27.
 
Terms and conditions apply; see think for details: https://bit.ly/3gmoMZ4

node.text:
HOT GIRL SUMMER GIVEAWAY 🌸

Win: 1 TAN + LINES bikini of your choice, 1 TAN + LINES bikini bag, 1 TAN + LINES muse towel, 1 $200 gift card to Winc & 1 $200 gift card to Funboy!

To enter: 
1. Like this post
2. Follow all three: @shoptanlines @funboy @winc
3. Tag a friend in the comments
You can enter as many times as you like (just be sure to tag a different friend each time!). Winner will be picked on 7/29 at 10am PST. Profile must be public to enter.
Legal stuff: 
Must be 21+ to enter and a U.S. resident
Gift card from Winc is exclusive of tax and shipping
Winc cannot ship wine to: AL, AK, AR, DE, HI, KY, MI, MS, NJ, RH, SD and UT
